testsuite.name: au.org.ala.ecodata.ReportingServiceSpec

testcase.name: Resetting a single activity report should delete associated output data
Resetting a report should fail if the report is submitted or approved
A submitted or approved report should not be able to be updated
A report of type adjustment cannot be adjusted
A report that is already adjusted cannot be adjusted again
Adjusting a report will create a new report of type Adjustment and update the status history of the original report
